<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q36_v2" title="Q36_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una librería, se modela la compra de cuadernos (<m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>) y lápices (<m:math><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:math>) con el siguiente sistema de ecuaciones:</p>
    <div>
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
    </div>
    <p>Según este modelo, ¿cuántos cuadernos y cuántos lápices se compraron?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si x = 4 e y = 5, entonces en la primera ecuación se obtiene 3·4 + 2·5 = 12 + 10 = 22, pero en la segunda ecuación se obtiene 4 + 5 = 9, y 9 ≠ 8. Por lo tanto, esta opción no satisface el sistema completo.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si x = 6 e y = 2, entonces 3·6 + 2·2 = 18 + 4 = 22 y además 6 + 2 = 8. Como satisface las dos ecuaciones, esta es la solución del sistema.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si x = 8 e y = 0, entonces en la primera ecuación se obtiene 3·8 + 2·0 = 24 + 0 = 24, y 24 ≠ 22. Aunque en la segunda ecuación 8 + 0 = 8, no basta con cumplir una sola ecuación. Esta opción no satisface el sistema completo.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si x = 4 e y = 4, entonces en la primera ecuación se obtiene 3·4 + 2·4 = 12 + 8 = 20, y 20 ≠ 22. Aunque en la segunda ecuación 4 + 4 = 8, esta opción no satisface las dos ecuaciones al mismo tiempo.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso por sustitución</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Despejar una variable en la ecuación más simple</strong></p>
            <p>De la ecuación</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>despejamos <m:math><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:math>:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sustituir en la otra ecuación</strong></p>
            <p>Reemplazamos <m:math><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:math> por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> en</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>y obtenemos:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Resolver la ecuación resultante</strong></p>
            <p>Distribuimos el 2:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Reducimos términos semejantes:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Restamos 16 en ambos lados:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Hallar el valor de y</strong></p>
            <p>Sustituimos <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> por 6 en</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Verificar la solución</strong></p>
            <p>Comprobamos en la primera ecuación:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Comprobamos en la segunda ecuación:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Se compraron 6 cuadernos y 2 lápices. La alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>